author: Russell Brand
description:
MSNBC is collapsing in real time. Their desperate rebrand to “MS Now” is being sold as “breaking news,” but it’s really just another marketing ploy to mask a failing business model and a history of state-friendly propaganda. From praising Biden as “the sharpest tack” to shilling for Big Pharma and global conglomerates, this network has long served elite interests, not the public. Legacy media is dying, and rather than reform, they double down with hollow rebrands. The real insurgency is independent media—where truth isn’t pre-chewed pap spoon-fed by corporations but uncovered, debated, and shared freely.
